    <briefdescription>
<para>Bit flags tracking successfully parsed fields from a PAX extended header. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>These flags indicate that a PAX keyword was both present in the block and successfully parsed into <ref refid="structmptar__metadata" kindref="compound">mptar_metadata</ref>. If keyword parsing fails, the respective bit is explicitly left unset. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
